  "title": "CONSTRUCTION SUPERVISOR",
  "description": "<p><p>Supervise daily construction and renovation activities on-site, ensuring work follows approved drawings and project specifications.</p></p><p><p>Coordinate and assign tasks to workers, subcontractors, and technical staff.</p></p><p><p>Monitor work progress and report updates to project managers or company management.</p></p><p><p>Ensure compliance with workplace safety regulations and company policies.</p></p><p><p>Inspect workmanship quality and resolve on-site issues promptly.</p></p><p><p>Maintain proper use, storage, and handling of materials, tools, and equipment.</p></p><p><p>Liaise with clients, designers, and contractors as necessary to ensure project requirements are met.</p></p><p><p>Keep accurate records of daily activities, incidents, and materials usage.</p></p>",
